---
title: "US54 — Admin log out"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as System Administrator
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>AdminShell
  participant C as «Control»<br/>Authenticate
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>Profile
  A->>B: tap LOG OUT
  B->>C: signOut()
  C->>E: signOut()
  E-->>C: session cleared
  C-->>B: state = AsyncData (signed out)
  B-->>A: redirect to LoginScreen
  note over E: signOut via AuthGateway → Supabase Auth.<br/>cached Profile cleared on sign-out
